    "description": "This rice bowl is small in size but big on flavour. You'll coat pulled chicken in a garlic and lime glaze before pairing it with a zingy corn and tomato salad and serving over fluffy brown rice. Smaller portion providing 2 of your 5-a-day and high in protein.",
